---
title: French-Style Lentils with Roasted Roots and Cheesy Garlic Bread
description: This French-inspired dish is a delight, bursting with aromatics from tarragon and the earthy tones of lentils. Then there's the warmth of wholegrain mustard and cheesy toasts on the side. It's a winner!
